  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BARTENDER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Overview:</strong></p>\n<p>In charge of all beverage and dessert making and preparation, and cutting of fruit for daily operation</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities and Duties:</strong></p>\n<p>- To prepare and serve alcoholic and non-alcoholic drinks consistently with company’s beverage standard.</p>\n<p>- Assist manager in the efficient running of the day-to-day operation including set up and closing of the bar counter.</p>\n<p>- Maintain bottles &amp; glasses in a functional manner to support efficient drink preparation and promotion of beverage.</p>\n<p>- Prepare and manage all dessert orders from serving staff</p>\n<p>- Cutting and preparation of fruits</p>\n<p>- Responsible for the cleanliness of the glasses, utensils, bar equipment &amp; station.</p>\n<p>- Take beverage orders from serving staff or directly from patrons accurately &amp; promptly.</p>\n<p>- Assist the restocking and replenishment of bar inventory and supplies.</p>\n<p>- Arrange beverage by FIFO (FIRST IN FIRST OUT) by dates.</p>\n<p>- Adhere to hygiene and safety standards</p>\n<p>- Adhere to company’s standard operating procedures</p>\n<p>- Any other appropriate duties and responsibilities as assigned</p>",
